<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.3">
<l>caṅku māmaiyun taḷaru mēṉimēl</l>
<l>tiṅkaḷ veṅkatir cīṟu meṉceykēṉ</l>
<l>poṅku veṇṭiraip puṇari vaṇṇaṉār</l>
<l>koṅka lārntatār kūvu meṉṉaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[My] conch [bangles] and complexion slip away;</l>
<l>The moon’s hot rays on my body burn. What do I do?</l>
<l>The nectar-filled garland of the one</l>
<l>The color of the sea with roiling white waves beckons me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
